<br />
<br />There was two prototypes for Dr. Mario, known by the name Virus for unknown reasons, those are the two revisions that still exist so far!
<br />
<br />One has MMC1 and one has NROM, a person at NintendoAge most possibly still owns both after buying them from Ebay, they are not dumped yet. (according to Lost Levels Forums), But I do not know who.
<br />
<br />That is a reason why it uses only a single 32k bank (or 2 16k banks) and 4 times the CHR amount the original source proto (NROM) has

		

